### Lanka Vacations API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### 2. Get All Destinations
GET http://localhost:5000/api/destinations

### 3. Get All Packages
GET http://localhost:5000/api/packages

### 4. Get Specific Package
GET http://localhost:5000/api/packages/pkg_001

### 5. Get Map Destinations
GET http://localhost:5000/api/map/destinations

### 6. Get Hotels (All)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/map/hotels

### 7. Get Hotels by Budget
GET http://localhost:5000/api/map/hotels?max_price=100

### 8. Get Hotels by Destination
GET http://localhost:5000/api/map/hotels?destination_id=dest_004

### 9. Get Package Route
GET http://localhost:5000/api/map/package/pkg_001/route

### 10. Generate Custom Itinerary
POST http://localhost:5000/api/itinerary/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "test-session-123",
  "interests": ["beach", "cultural", "wildlife"],
  "budget": "1500",
  "exact_days": 7,
  "preferred_destinations": ["Kandy", "Mirissa", "Yala"],
  "accommodation_type": "standard",
  "starting_point": "Colombo"
}

### 11. Get Itinerary Map Data (replace :id with actual response_id from above)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/itinerary/REPLACE_WITH_ID/map-data

### 12. Get Activities
GET http://localhost:5000/api/activities

### ADMIN ENDPOINTS (Require JWT Token)
### First, you need to implement admin login to get token

### 13. Create Destination (Admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/destinations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "destination_name": "Jaffna",
  "type": "city",
  "description": "Northern cultural capital of Sri Lanka",
  "latitude": 9.6615,
  "longitude": 80.0255,
  "best_visit_start": "jan",
  "best_visit_end": "dec",
  "tags": ["Cultural", "Tamil", "Northern"],
  "image_url": "https://example.com/jaffna.jpg"
}

### 14. Create Hotel (Admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/hotels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "hotel_name": "Test Beach Resort",
  "destination_id": "dest_016",
  "type": "4_star_superior",
  "address": "Beach Road, Mirissa",
  "price_per_night_usd": 120,
  "room_types": ["single", "double", "suite"],
  "meal_plans": ["breakfast_only", "half_board"],
  "amenities": ["wifi", "pool", "restaurant", "spa"],
  "image_urls": ["https://example.com/hotel1.jpg"],
  "contact_email": "info@testresort.com",
  "contact_phone": "+94771234567"
}

### 15. Get All Admin Destinations
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/destinations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 16. Get All Admin Hotels
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/hotels
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
